{
  "text": "Finite element method (FEM) simulations are carried out to verify the proposed concepts. The configuration of the unit cell is shown in Figure 8a . The unit cell consists of aluminum substrate (size 5\u00d75\u00d71 mm [CITATION_1] ) and a piezoelectric transducer (size 4\u00d74\u00d70.8 mm 3 ) bonded on its surface. An inductor is connected to the top and bottom surfaces of the piezoelectric transducer as the shunt circuit.",
